name: Can't hurt me
author: David googings
description: It follows David's life from his hard and trauma-filled childhood all the way to his becoming one of the world's best endurance athletes and a motivational speaker. The author truly believes that anyone can realize their potential through discipline, persistence, and mental toughness.

name: When Breath Becomes Air
author: Paul Kalanithi
description: When Breath Becomes Air chronicles Kalanithi's transformation from a naïve medical student “possessed,” as he wrote, “by the question of what, given that all organisms die, makes a virtuous and meaningful life” into a neurosurgeon at Stanford working in the brain, the most critical place for human identity
